headline: Triumph Group Q3 Earnings Beat Estimates, Sales Increase Y/Y
summary: TGI's total sales in the third quarter of fiscal 2025 surpass the Zacks Consensus Estimate by 10.1%. The top line also increases 10.7% from the year-ago level.
